description: This unemployment rate data comes from the Bureau of Labot Statistics Local Area Unemployment Statistics (LAUS), which are published on a monthly basis.  It is not seasonally adjusted. It includes data for the following counties: Orleans Parish, LA (New Orleans); Oklahoma County, OK (Oklahoma City); Hillsborough County, FL (Tampa); Wake County, NC (Raleigh); Fulton County, GA (Atlanta); Miami-Dade County, FL (Miami); Davidson County, TN (Nashville); Shelby County, TN (Memphis); Jefferson County, KY (Louisiville). This data covers the time period of 2005 to present.
